   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#6484006443309841895_57213-h-3.htm.html#FNanchor_43" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">43)</text:span></text:a> Öt körmön, azaz ragadoz.</text:p>
